### Crowdfunding App - Comprehensive API Tests
### RestClient Extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ========================================
### AUTH FLOW - START HERE
### ========================================

### 1. REGISTER NEW USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### Save the OTP from email/console output

### ========================================
### 2. VERIFY OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@gmail.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### ========================================
### 3. LOGIN USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "activeRole": "Donor"
}

### Save the token from response above
@userToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImQyODcxYjQ1LTUwNmItNGZmMy1hY2I4LTVmZjFhZDJjNGU5MSIsImVtYWlsIjoidGVzdEBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiRG9ub3IiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUwNzM3NTEsImV4cCI6MTc3NTA3NzM1MX0.9lsz_vXhbNYZFzs3QxIxAmVqUHvrVlKX9lpF2l0kCPM

### ========================================
### 4. GET CURRENT USER
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

### ========================================
### 5. LOGOUT USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

### ========================================
### USER MANAGEMENT APIS
### ========================================

### 6. GET YOUR PROFILE
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

### ========================================
### 7. UPDATE YOUR PROFILE
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Johnny",
  "lastName": "Doe Updated",
  "phone": "03001234567"
}

### ========================================
### 8. GET ALL USERS (ADMIN ONLY)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/all
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 9. DELETE YOUR ACCOUNT
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

### ========================================
### APPLICATION APIS
### ========================================

### 10. SUBMIT APPLICATION (DONOR ONLY)
POST {{baseUrl}}/application
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

{
  "phone": "03009876543",
  "work_email": "donor@work.com",
  "address": "456 Oak Street, Lahore, Pakistan",
  "facebook_url": "https://facebook.com/newuser",
  "instagram_url": "https://instagram.com/newuser",
  "linkedin_url": "https://linkedin.com/in/newuser"
}

### ========================================
### 11. GET YOUR APPLICATIONS
GET {{baseUrl}}/application/my
Cookie: token={{userToken}}

### ========================================
### 12. GET ALL APPLICATIONS (ADMIN ONLY)
GET {{baseUrl}}/application/all
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 13. APPROVE/REJECT APPLICATION (ADMIN ONLY)
### Replace APP_ID with actual application UUID
POST {{baseUrl}}/application/APP_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "Approved"
}

### ========================================
### NOTES
### ========================================
### 1. Replace newuser@gmail.com with your desired email
### 2. Check your email or console for OTP (if using Mailtrap/Mock)
### 3. Replace @userToken with actual token from login response
### 4. Replace ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE with an admin user's token
### 5. Replace APP_ID with real application UUID from database
### 6. To use variables: Select line and press Ctrl+Alt+E (or use variable)
